{"id":14496,"date":"2023-02-16T21:38:02","date_gmt":"2023-02-17T05:38:02","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/198.199.80.40\/?p=14496"},"modified":"2023-02-17T14:10:49","modified_gmt":"2023-02-17T22:10:49","slug":"4-ways-hosting-wordpress-cheap","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/truewealth.moneyvikings.com\/2023\/02\/4-ways-hosting-wordpress-cheap\/","title":{"rendered":"4 Ways to Hosting WordPress on a Shoestring Budget"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>There are many ways to host a blog, and as Financial Bloggers we pride ourselves on running a blog on the cheap. We\u2764\ufe0f Linux!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-rank-math-toc-block\" id=\"rank-math-toc\"><h2>Table of Contents<\/h2><nav><ul><li><a href=\"#hosting-wordpress-option-1-free-blogger-or-blogspot\">Hosting WordPress: Option 1 : Free : Blogger or Blogspot<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"#hosting-wordpress-option-2-paid-digital-ocean\">Hosting WordPress: Option 2: Paid : Digital Ocean<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"#hosting-wordpress-option-3-vultr-virtual-machine\">Hosting WordPress: Option 3 : Vultr Virtual Machine<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"#hosting-wordpress-option-4-wordpress-com-hosting\">Hosting WordPress Option 4 : WordPress.com Hosting<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"#you-may-also-enjoy-these-free-a-href-https-truewealth-moneyvikings-com-truewealth-moneyvikings-com-a-articles\">You May Also Enjoy These Free truewealth.moneyvikings.com articles&#8230;<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"hosting-wordpress-option-1-free-blogger-or-blogspot\">Hosting WordPress: Option 1 : Free : Blogger or Blogspot<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Yes we could certainly go with <a href=\"https:\/\/blogger.com\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https:\/\/blogger.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">blogger<\/a> and <a href=\"http:\/\/blogger.com\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"blogger.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">blogspot<\/a> for free and not have to worry about hosting wordpress on your own, but you give up a bit of control and predictability with that. (And technically it&#8217;s not WordPress).  In the end we decided to host on our own linux cloud virtual machines.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"hosting-wordpress-option-2-paid-digital-ocean\">Hosting WordPress: Option 2: Paid : Digital Ocean<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the best deals I could find out there was <a href=\"https:\/\/www.digitalocean.com\/?refcode=db00a34f913a&amp;utm_campaign=Referral_Invite&amp;utm_medium=Referral_Program&amp;utm_source=badge\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https:\/\/www.digitalocean.com\/?refcode=db00a34f913a&amp;utm_campaign=Referral_Invite&amp;utm_medium=Referral_Program&amp;utm_source=badge\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Digital Ocean<\/a>, running their 1 CPU \/ 1 GB RAM \/ 25 GB Storage Virtual Machine for $6\/month. Once you have it setup, download and install wordpress and send traffic to your blog. Use a free domain name registrar, or sign-up with hover for domain name hosting on your own, but that will cost another 10$-$20\/year for your own custom domain.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"305\" src=\"http:\/\/198.199.80.40\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/Screenshot-2023-02-16-at-9.00.46-PM-1024x305.png\" alt=\"hosting wordpress\" class=\"wp-image-14524\" srcset=\"https:\/\/truewealth.moneyvikings.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/Screenshot-2023-02-16-at-9.00.46-PM-1024x305.png 1024w, https:\/\/truewealth.moneyvikings.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/Screenshot-2023-02-16-at-9.00.46-PM-300x89.png 300w, https:\/\/truewealth.moneyvikings.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/Screenshot-2023-02-16-at-9.00.46-PM-768x229.png 768w, https:\/\/truewealth.moneyvikings.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/Screenshot-2023-02-16-at-9.00.46-PM-1536x457.png 1536w, https:\/\/truewealth.moneyvikings.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/Screenshot-2023-02-16-at-9.00.46-PM-2048x610.png 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Not the cheapest virtual machine in the mix, but reasonable for our needs right now.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"hosting-wordpress-option-3-vultr-virtual-machine\">Hosting WordPress: Option 3 : Vultr Virtual Machine<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you really want a deal, look at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.vultr.com\/?ref=7140906\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">vultr<\/a> and get the $2.50\/month instance with 1 CPU, .5 GB RAM, and spin up an ipv6 only for the cheapest of the cheap VMs. We use one of theirs for a test instance for trying out new themes, plugins, and ideas before promoting to our production instance.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"858\" src=\"http:\/\/198.199.80.40\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/Screenshot-2023-02-16-at-9.04.50-PM-1024x858.png\" alt=\"hosting wordpress\" class=\"wp-image-14525\" srcset=\"https:\/\/truewealth.moneyvikings.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/Screenshot-2023-02-16-at-9.04.50-PM-1024x858.png 1024w, https:\/\/truewealth.moneyvikings.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/Screenshot-2023-02-16-at-9.04.50-PM-300x251.png 300w, https:\/\/truewealth.moneyvikings.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/Screenshot-2023-02-16-at-9.04.50-PM-768x643.png 768w, https:\/\/truewealth.moneyvikings.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/Screenshot-2023-02-16-at-9.04.50-PM-1536x1287.png 1536w, https:\/\/truewealth.moneyvikings.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/Screenshot-2023-02-16-at-9.04.50-PM-2048x1716.png 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This modest virtual machine on Digital Ocean can run for hours and hours without problems running WordPress and Apache. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"935\" src=\"http:\/\/198.199.80.40\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/Screenshot-2023-02-16-at-9.08.45-PM-1024x935.png\" alt=\"wordpress hosting\" class=\"wp-image-14526\" srcset=\"https:\/\/truewealth.moneyvikings.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/Screenshot-2023-02-16-at-9.08.45-PM-1024x935.png 1024w, https:\/\/truewealth.moneyvikings.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/Screenshot-2023-02-16-at-9.08.45-PM-300x274.png 300w, https:\/\/truewealth.moneyvikings.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/Screenshot-2023-02-16-at-9.08.45-PM-768x701.png 768w, https:\/\/truewealth.moneyvikings.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/Screenshot-2023-02-16-at-9.08.45-PM-1536x1402.png 1536w, https:\/\/truewealth.moneyvikings.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/Screenshot-2023-02-16-at-9.08.45-PM.png 1724w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A day in the life of <a href=\"http:\/\/198.199.80.40\" target=\"_blank\">http:\/\/198.199.80.40<\/a><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>(Unless a nasty robot attacks you). WordPress is free, just download it, host it, and pay for the monthly VM Cloud Hosting.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"hosting-wordpress-option-4-wordpress-com-hosting\">Hosting WordPress Option 4 : WordPress.com Hosting<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You  can currently do this <a href=\"https:\/\/wordpress.com\/pricing\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">for free, or as cheap as $4.99\/month<\/a> <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Now we need to get back to work and continue on our journey writing about financial freedom.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"you-may-also-enjoy-these-free-a-href-https-truewealth-moneyvikings-com-truewealth-moneyvikings-com-a-articles\">You May Also Enjoy These Free <a href=\"http:\/\/198.199.80.40\" target=\"_blank\">truewealth.moneyvikings.com<\/a> articles&#8230;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-money-vikings wp-block-embed-money-vikings\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\nhttp:\/\/19